[Amit Varma]: Russ, thank you so much for coming on The Scene and The Unseen, it's been a great honor

01:45:29.440 --> 01:45:30.440
[Guest]: for me.

01:45:30.440 --> 01:45:31.440
[Guest]: It was great, Amit.

01:45:31.440 --> 01:45:32.440
[Guest]: Loved it.

